    "description": "TRADE WORKS Co., Ltd. engages in system development, cloud service provision, system maintenance and operation services. The company offers financial solutions, such as trade agent, a trading system for internet customers of securities companies that supports products such as stocks, derivatives, FX, credit cards, investment trusts, bonds, and crypto assets, and PC and smartphone; a trade monitoring system which monitors fraudulent transactions specific to financial products, including fraudulent price formation and insider trading; and fixed-point monitoring for real-time monitoring. It also provides a digital commerce solution, consisting of EC platforms, embedded development using API connections, content development using XR technology; digital solutions, including blockchain-based digital advertising; and MetaVillage, a metaverse platform used for two-way communication through avatars. In addition, the company engages in development, maintenance and operation of systems for FX companies, and provides maintenance and operation services after product installation; and offers a foreign exchange margin trading system business, which consists of Trading Studio, an online foreign exchange margin trading system for investors. Further, it provides server and network design and construction services; system services; and software contract development and concierge services. Additionally, it offers investment advisory, and security services. TRADE WORKS Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
